.If a item is illegal in the system change it so it isn't produced in the system.cataport custom officers that scan you when you enter the system for illegal goods with the options to declare you dont have any illegal goods, bribe like at stations or engage in battle with the custom. if detection is positive the option to drop cargo with no fine, or battle.Trade route between star systems could do with a bit of a polish its hard to do a trade run when you cant really see what a system sells/buys my solution would be the that you can view other star systems you have visited via the galactic map by clicking on it.crew.now unless i am mistaken the max crew you can have is 8 this is simply not enough for some of the larger ships (note this is an asumption as i dont have this ship yet), take the sharkalon the most expensive ship in the game and a ship thats designed to be combat orintated the problem is with its 4 turrets 2 cannons and 2 torpedos so 8 crew members to man the guns in battle the problem is who pilots the ship in battle everyone is maning guns who hacks who operates the sheilds for a ship thats designed for combat your rather short staffed to really funtion effectively.solution is simples the bigger the ship the more crew you can hire.combatmore combat options would be a nice touch such as targeting wepons or engins. mines to slow down those fast raiders chacing your slow frighter would be awesome as well"
